{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/yz5dz3","slide":1,"text":"All Risk, No Reward is a consent-first social courage app. It turns one healthy, uncomfortable action into a daily game—without public shame, forced posting, or reckless dares."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/2ssgt3","slide":2,"title":"THE ACTUAL PROBLEM","textShapes":12}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/yt8vupsr","slide":2,"text":"THE ACTUAL PROBLEM","textPreview":"THE ACTUAL PROBLEM","textChars":18,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,40,520,22]}
