{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/kvadwzax","slide":2,"text":"The gap between “I should” and “I did” eats every good intention.","textPreview":"The gap between “I should” and “I did” eats every good intention.","textChars":65,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,232,480,72]}
