{"kind":"image","id":"im/by9snqh0","slide":2,"name":"","geometry":"rect","alt":"Landing page showing the social courage challenge card and demo call to action","bbox":[650,42,520,438]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/2ssgt3","slide":2,"text":"The problem is not a lack of advice. It is the infinite delay between intention and action. The app closes that gap with a randomized daytime unlock, one concrete task, and a real deadline."}
