{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/kzrc58","slide":3,"text":"The entire product is one short loop: the app deals one challenge, the user records privacy-safe proof, and the system scores the evidence. The result feeds points, streaks, levels, milestones, and a private history—not a public social graph."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/evfu5z","slide":4,"title":"PROOF WITHOUT SURVEILLANCE","textShapes":15}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/9cvmd07m","slide":4,"text":"PROOF WITHOUT SURVEILLANCE","textPreview":"PROOF WITHOUT SURVEILLANCE","textChars":26,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,42,520,22]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/mpkn2l8b","slide":4,"text":"AI scores evidence—\nnot your worth.","textPreview":"AI scores evidence— | not your worth.","textChars":35,"textLines":2,"bbox":[64,88,520,120]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/7qt4bqpg","slide":4,"text":"The system asks: did a concrete action happen? It never asks whether you were charismatic enough.","textPreview":"The system asks: did a concrete action happen? It never asks whether you were charismatic enough.","textChars":97,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,232,500,84]}
