{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/evfu5z","slide":4,"text":"Proof is designed to be useful without becoming surveillance. In local demo mode, a transparent concrete-detail heuristic runs in the browser. In hosted mode, the user must explicitly consent before Gemini receives the note or optional media through the secure backend proxy."}
{"kind":"slide","id":"sl/lj7xih","slide":5,"title":"FAILURE IS A GAME STATE, NOT A CHARACTER FLAW","textShapes":12}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/29gjuh0r","slide":5,"text":"FAILURE IS A GAME STATE, NOT A CHARACTER FLAW","textPreview":"FAILURE IS A GAME STATE, NOT A CHARACTER FLAW","textChars":45,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,40,520,22]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/pc72pcj2","slide":5,"text":"Missed it? The app\nrolls dice. Literally.","textPreview":"Missed it? The app | rolls dice. Literally.","textChars":41,"textLines":2,"bbox":[64,82,590,128]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/oby1w7ix","slide":5,"text":"A partial or missed challenge creates a bounded, private recovery task—then makes closing the loop weirdly compelling.","textPreview":"A partial or missed challenge creates a bounded, private recovery task—then makes closing the loop weirdly compelling.","textChars":118,"textLines":1,"bbox":[64,232,500,82]}
