{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/lj7xih","slide":5,"text":"The app does not pretend every attempt is perfect. Partial or missed challenges create a private recovery task. Users get two irreversible, no-repeat dice rerolls that can get easier or harder. Completing the recovery—or spending a lifeline—closes the loop."}
